N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 2 ยง 123.5 - Manual reporting instructions

State Regulations

Reports filed manually on form AC 2686 must be typewritten
and shall be prepared in accordance with the instructions for preparing
abandoned property reports--as set forth in the Handbook for Reporters of
